    "description": "Maruyama Mfg. Co., Inc. manufactures and sells machinery in Japan and internationally. The company offers agricultural machines, such as brush cutters, furrow trimmers, riding and self-propelled grass cutters, power sprayers, backpack portable power sprayers, manual pest control machines, power spreaders, ditch cutters, aerial and electric work platforms, and rice related products; riding and large pest control machines, including stereo and boom sprayers, high creation boom, multirotor for liquid spraying, multi and shuttle sprayers, and freshhousers; green related products, comprising chainsaws, hedge trimmers, blowers, chippers, and shredders; pumps, cleaning machines, and mist generators, such as pump motor sets, industrial pumps, high pressure washers, and disinfection equipment; and fire extinguishers and disaster prevention equipment. It also provides ultra fine bubble related products, which includes ultra pumps, washing machines, ultra coolant freshers, mounted generators, and general water supply installation; power spreaders; agricultural drones; and engine pumps and cleaners. In addition, the company involved in the contract design, construction of plumbing, and real estate and leasing activities. It was formerly known as Maruyama Shokai and changed its name to Maruyama Mfg. Co., Inc. in 1937. Maruyama Mfg. Co., Inc. was founded in 1895 and is headquartered in Chiyoda, Japan."
